phonebook {
    Canonical project links live in ["./phonebook.json"].
    Modules that need contact, repo, or marketplace URLs should read from there instead of hardcoding values.
    Typed access is shared via ["../../scripts/phonebook.ts"] for the site and extension README generator.
}

extension_readme_links {
    The extension VSIX README uses phonebook link ids `github`, `vsc`, `openvsx`, and `email` for repository, marketplace, Open VSX, and contact URLs.
    Generation is defined in ["../distribution/distribution.rq".extension_readme].
}
